Package: gamVineCopula
Type: Package
Title: Generalized additive models for conditional dependence structures and
    Vine copulas
Version: 0.0-1
Date: 2014-08-05
Author: Thibault Vatter
Maintainer: Thibault Vatter <thibault.vatter@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    VineCopula (>= 1.3),
    mgcv (>= 1.8-2),
    MASS,
    gsl,
    methods
Suggests:
    copula
Description: This package implements various inference and simulation tools to
    apply generalized additive models to bivariate dependence structures and
    vine copulas.
